    <string name="what_are_spaces_and_groups_title">What are Spaces and Groups:</string>
    <string name="what_are_spaces_and_groups_info">- A Space is an area which contains Devices, like a room in a house. A Group is a collection of Devices, for example some wall lamps in the living room that also contains ceiling lamps</string>
    <string name="what_can_a_space_do_title">What can a Space do:</string>
    <string name="what_can_a_space_do_info">- A Space can be controlled on the Home Screen\n- It can be nested in another Space so that it can be controlled as part of the larger Space.\n- A Space can have Scenes and Schedules\n- Sensors and Switches can be set up to control a Space</string>
    <string name="what_can_a_group_do_title">What can a Group do:</string>
    <string name="what_can_a_group_do_info">- A Group must be nested in a Space or another Group to be controlled\n- A Group can only have Schedules\n- Sensors and Switches can be set up to control a Group</string>
